OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,FWomen with signs of womb cancer can be
OL,7,Foffered a less invasive test to rule
OL,8,Fout disease after it was given the
OL,9,Fgreen light for use in the UK.
OL,11,FThe new test, WID-easy, uses some of
OL,12,Fthe same technology used in Covid PCR
OL,13,Ftests.
OL,15,FTraditionally, women with signs of
OL,16,Fwomb cancer would need a transvaginal
OL,17,Fultrasound scan or a hysteroscopy `
OL,18,Fwhere a tube with a camera in it is
OL,19,Fused to look inside the womb ` to
OL,20,Fconfirm or rule out disease.
