OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,FThe new PCR (polymerase chain
OL,7,Freaction) test is a simple swab, which
OL,8,Fis sent off to a laboratory for
OL,9,Fanalysis.
OL,11,FScientists then look for changes in
OL,12,Fthe DNA that indicate whether womb
OL,13,Fcancer is present or not.
OL,15,FIf the test indicates that a woman has
OL,16,Fwomb cancer, then the woman would need
OL,17,Fa biopsy to confirm or rule out the
OL,18,Fdiagnosis.
