OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,FThe test, by University College London
OL,7,F(UCL) spinout company Sola
OL,8,FDiagnostics, has been approved for use
OL,9,Fin the UK by the Medicines and
OL,10,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,11,F(MHRA) for women over the age of 45
OL,12,Fwho have abnormal uterine bleeding.
OL,14,FThis means that it is immediately
OL,15,Favailable to private clinics, and it
OL,16,Fis hoped that it will one day be made
OL,17,Favailable for widespread use on the
OL,18,FNHS.
