OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,FAnalysis of the test, which was
OL,7,Fdeveloped by researchers from UCL and
OL,8,Fthe University of Innsbruck, was
OL,9,Fpublished in the Lancet Oncology in
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FThe study found that the WID-easy test
OL,13,Fdetects the same number of women with
OL,14,Fwomb cancer as ultrasound.
OL,16,F"The... test delivers fast results and
OL,17,Fshows improved performance compared
OL,18,Fwith a combination of imaging index
OL,19,Ftests," the authors wrote at the time.
