OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,FThe test also significantly reduces
OL,7,Fthe number of false positives, which
OL,8,Fcould mean that fewer healthy women
OL,9,Fwould be sent to have invasive
OL,10,Fhysteroscopy or biopsy procedures.
OL,12,FInventor of the test, Professor Martin
OL,13,FWidschwendter, from UCL's Institute
OL,14,Ffor Women's Health and the University
OL,15,Fof Innsbruck in Austria, said: "The
OL,16,FWID-easy test is the first test of its
OL,17,Fkind in the UK ` using a simple swab
OL,18,Fmethod to detect womb cancer.
