OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,F"We are proud to have developed a test
OL,7,Fthat addresses an urgent gap in
OL,8,Fwomen's health and performs well
OL,9,Facross all women."
OL,11,FAthena Lamnisos, chief executive of
OL,12,FThe Eve Appeal, added: "Currently in
OL,13,Fthe UK, the tests to investigate
OL,14,Fabnormal bleeding and check for womb
OL,15,Fcancer can cause stress and
OL,16,Fdiscomfort. The usual test is a
OL,17,Fhysteroscopy, which many find painful
OL,18,Fand invasive.
OL,20,F"A test which is less painful and more
OL,21,Facceptable is to be welcomed by many.
