OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,F"One of the key groups who may benefit
OL,7,Ffrom this test are Black women who
OL,8,Fmore often receive a late-stage
OL,9,Fdiagnosis for this cancer.
OL,11,F"The Eve Appeal is delighted to see
OL,12,Fthis progress in research that the
OL,13,Fcharity funded, resulting in a test
OL,14,Fthat may be effective in the clinical
OL,15,Fsetting.
