OL,3,CNew less invasive cancer test by
OL,4,CLondon doctors to check for womb cancer
OL,6,F"The WID-easy test could enable the
OL,7,Fmany thousands of women who experience
OL,8,Fabnormal bleeding, and where cancer
OL,9,Fneeds to be ruled out, to potentially
OL,10,Favoid painful tests like
OL,11,Fhysteroscopies and have their minds
OL,12,Fput at rest sooner, saving them from
OL,13,Funnecessary stress."
